Package: bioshmods
Title: Shiny Modules for Bioinformatics Data Exploration
Version: 0.1.4.9004
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "January",
           family = "Weiner",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "january.weiner@bih-charite.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1438-7819"))
Description: Reusable shiny modules and helper functions for interactive
    exploration of high throughput bioinformatic analyses. The package provides
    components for result tables, gene expression profiles, volcano and disco
    plots, PCA views, gene-set enrichment browsing, gene-group selection, and
    export of tabular or generic R objects. It also includes example COVID-19
    data ('C19').
